name: Lando System? (V)
Lore: '''Lando''s not a system, he''s a man.'' Regardless of where Rebels flee, dark agents are sure to follow.',
Text: 'Take Lando or a card with ''Lando'' in game text into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Cancel an attempt to replace your Lando; opponent''s Lando is lost.',
